==English==
===Noun===
'''Parquebot'''
# ([[postal history]]) [[cancellation mark]] printed on letters posted at sea before delivery to the [[postal]] authorities at the next port of call.
===Adjective===
#Relating to mail posted at sea.
#: a '''Parquebot''' letter, a '''Parquebot''' [[duplex]].
===Usage Note===
#The word would typically be stamped in upper case, '''PARQUEBOT''', on the postal item, but when described in text would be written with a capital P only, eg, '''Parquebot'''.
